==English==

===Noun===
'''aptness'''
# [[fitness|Fitness]]; [[suitableness]]; [[appropriateness]]; as, the aptness of things to their end.
# [[disposition|Disposition]] of the [[mind]]; [[propensity]]; as, the aptness of men to follow example.
# Quickness of [[apprehension]]; readiness in learning; [[docility]]; as, an aptness to learn is more observable in some children than in others.
# [[proneness|Proneness]]; [[tendency]]; as, the aptness of iron to rust.

